comment scan operator (running reduce)
comment prefix sums
quad assign +\ 1 2 3 4
comment running product
quad assign *\ 1 2 3 4 5
comment running max
quad assign ceil\ 3 1 4 1 5 9
comment running min
quad assign floor\ 9 5 1 4 3
comment running or
quad assign or\ 0 0 1 0 0
comment running and
quad assign and\ 1 1 1 0 1
